      "title": "Doppler AVF Ultrasound Scan | Cadabams Diagnostics ",
      "description": "Book a painless 30-minute Doppler AVF ultrasound scan at Cadabams Diagnostics to check fistula flow, detect stenosis, and safeguard dialysis access.",
